Class MapPropertySet.Definition<V>

  • java.lang.Object

    public class MapPropertySet.Definition<V>
extends Object
implements PropertyDefinition<Map<String,Object>,V>
    A PropertyDefinition within a MapPropertySet.

    Instances provide MapPropertySet.Definition.Getters that allow recovery of the originating instance; see MapPropertySet.propertyDefinitionForBinding().
